location.address: N. Male Atoll, Kuda Villingili Resort Maldives

descriptions.direction: Located in Kuda Villingili, Kuda Villingili Maldives, Free Return Transfers 03 nights & above is near the airport and on a private beach. Chickens Break is another place to visit that comes recommended. Discover the area's water adventures with windsurfing and swimming nearby, or enjoy the great outdoors with hiking/biking trails.
descriptions.general: The Kuda Villingili Resort Maldives is a hotel. - LocationKuda Villingili Resort Maldives is located in North Malé Atoll, just a 30-minute luxuryboat ride away from Velana International Airport (MLE). Speedboat is the most convenient, comfortable, safe, and hassle-free transfer to the resort. Located on a 1-kilometre coral island called Kudavillingili, Kudavillingili is shaped by a global team of design talents working closely with the GHM team. Maldivian architecture anchors the resort’s overarching aesthetic appeal, with complementary interior design and landscaping from Singapore and a lighting scheme from the USA. The property is in desirable proximity to the Malé International Airport, a 25-minute speedboat ride away. Private transfers are available to and from Velena International airport.RoomThe 96 guest villas have something for everyone. From Deluxe Haven , Sky Haven and stand-alone beach villas & suites offers the space you require and proximity to the beach, to over-water villas with privacy and direct sea access, every option is an inspiration. Water and beach villas provides a king-sized double bed (twin bed on request), a safe deposit box, workspace with charging stations, private terrace/patio with sunbeds, minibar, espresso machine plus complimentary tea and coffee, complimentary Wi-Fi, flats-creen IPTV, mobile app for smart devices, in-villa tablet, soundbar, outdoor rain shower, indoor bathroom with rainshower and bathtub, bathrobe, kimono, slippers, beach bag available for use in villa, bathroom amenities, turndown services, mood lighting, and electricity wattage of 220VAC, 50Hz with universal socket outlets. AmenitiesThe Kudavillingili will launch a spa with eight overwater treatment rooms, a beach club and bar, an all-day dining restaurant and Hawkers Stalls featuring four live cooking stations. The Restaurant – serves the freshest, handcrafted food for breakfast and dinner, in an exclusive, classy ambience The Hawkers is located by the swimming pool and is an upscale dining venue serving up soulful, sharing style creations. There’s a bar and three distinct restaurants, Spice, East and Med, that serve mouth-watering Indian Arabic, Thai-Japanese and Italian-Mediterranean fusion street food through each restaurant’s open kitchens. The Resort houses two bars - the Main Bar and the Pool-side bar - offering classic cocktails, mocktails and hand-crafted beers. Indulge by the pool sipping on refreshing hand-crafted concoctions while the DJ mixes and the sun caresses. Hotel features beach bar, Cigar lounge, library, and spa. Recreational opportunities on the island run the gamut from courts for several different sports to surfing and a plethora of on-the-water and underwater pursuits.NOTE: "Rates Including transfers are subject to availability & extra charges in case of excess baggage".
